{"pageProps":{"post":{"id":"151","date":"2009. 1. 14. 14:46","title":"Windows7 VirtualBox에 설치해봤습니다.","content":"Windows의 새버전을 체험할 수 있도록 MS에서 다운로드를 할 수 있다기에 한번 다운로드 받아서 설치해보았습니다. 물론 남아도는 (좋은 사양의) 컴퓨터가 없기때문에 가장 성능좋은 컴퓨터에 VirtualBox로 설치했습니다.<br>\n<br>1. 부팅<br>\n<div class=\"imageblock center\" style=\"text-align: center; clear: both;\"><span data-url=\"https://t1.daumcdn.net/tistoryfile/fs13/4_tistory_2009_01_14_14_29_496d7822b0f08?x-content-disposition=inline\" data-lightbox=\"lightbox\"><img srcset=\"https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?scode=mtistory2&fname=https%3A%2F%2Ft1.daumcdn.net%2Ftistoryfile%2Ffs13%2F4_tistory_2009_01_14_14_29_496d7822b0f08%3Fx-content-disposition%3Dinline\" src=\"https://t1.daumcdn.net/tistoryfile/fs13/4_tistory_2009_01_14_14_29_496d7822b0f08?x-content-disposition=inline\" style=\"cursor: pointer;max-width:100%;height:auto\" width=\"510\" height=\"385\" alt=\"\" filename=\"screenshot9.png\" filemime=\"\" ></span></div><br>\n2. 언어 및 입력기 설정 (언어는 영어뿐이지만 입력기는 한글이 가능하네요)<br>\n<div class=\"imageblock center\" style=\"text-align: center; clear: both;\"><span data-url=\"https://t1.daumcdn.net/tistoryfile/fs13/35_tistory_2009_01_14_14_28_496d781a9bf57?x-content-disposition=inline\" data-lightbox=\"lightbox\"><img srcset=\"https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?scode=mtistory2&fname=https%3A%2F%2Ft1.daumcdn.net%2Ftistoryfile%2Ffs13%2F35_tistory_2009_01_14_14_28_496d781a9bf57%3Fx-content-disposition%3Dinline\" src=\"https://t1.daumcdn.net/tistoryfile/fs13/35_tistory_2009_01_14_14_28_496d781a9bf57?x-content-disposition=inline\" style=\"cursor: pointer;max-width:100%;height:auto\" width=\"510\" height=\"380\" alt=\"\" filename=\"screenshot11.png\" filemime=\"\" ></span></div><br>\n3. 설치 시작<br>\n<div class=\"imageblock center\" style=\"text-align: center; clear: both;\"><span data-url=\"https://t1.daumcdn.net/tistoryfile/fs13/23_tistory_2009_01_14_14_28_496d781ab65e4?x-content-disposition=inline\" data-lightbox=\"lightbox\"><img srcset=\"https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?scode=mtistory2&fname=https%3A%2F%2Ft1.daumcdn.net%2Ftistoryfile%2Ffs13%2F23_tistory_2009_01_14_14_28_496d781ab65e4%3Fx-content-disposition%3Dinline\" src=\"https://t1.daumcdn.net/tistoryfile/fs13/23_tistory_2009_01_14_14_28_496d781ab65e4?x-content-disposition=inline\" style=\"cursor: pointer;max-width:100%;height:auto\" width=\"510\" height=\"384\" alt=\"\" filename=\"screenshot12.png\" filemime=\"\" ></span></div><br>\n4. 라이센스에 동의하라! 는 말이..<br>\n<div class=\"imageblock center\" style=\"text-align: center; clear: both;\"><span data-url=\"https://t1.daumcdn.net/tistoryfile/fs13/22_tistory_2009_01_14_14_28_496d781ac5525?x-content-disposition=inline\" data-lightbox=\"lightbox\"><img srcset=\"https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?scode=mtistory2&fname=https%3A%2F%2Ft1.daumcdn.net%2Ftistoryfile%2Ffs13%2F22_tistory_2009_01_14_14_28_496d781ac5525%3Fx-content-disposition%3Dinline\" src=\"https://t1.daumcdn.net/tistoryfile/fs13/22_tistory_2009_01_14_14_28_496d781ac5525?x-content-disposition=inline\" style=\"cursor: pointer;max-width:100%;height:auto\" width=\"510\" height=\"381\" alt=\"\" filename=\"screenshot13.png\" filemime=\"\" ></span></div><br>\n5. Upgrade할지 Custom 설치를 할지 물어보는데 Upgrade를 선택했더니 할 수 없다고 나오네요. 당연하지만... :) Custom 으로 설치하는 것이 새 설치인가봅니다.<br>\n<div class=\"imageblock center\" style=\"text-align: center; clear: both;\"><span data-url=\"https://t1.daumcdn.net/tistoryfile/fs13/16_tistory_2009_01_14_14_29_496d781fd569b?x-content-disposition=inline\" data-lightbox=\"lightbox\"><img srcset=\"https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?scode=mtistory2&fname=https%3A%2F%2Ft1.daumcdn.net%2Ftistoryfile%2Ffs13%2F16_tistory_2009_01_14_14_29_496d781fd569b%3Fx-content-disposition%3Dinline\" src=\"https://t1.daumcdn.net/tistoryfile/fs13/16_tistory_2009_01_14_14_29_496d781fd569b?x-content-disposition=inline\" style=\"cursor: pointer;max-width:100%;height:auto\" width=\"510\" height=\"381\" alt=\"\" filename=\"screenshot14.png\" filemime=\"\" ></span></div><br>\n6. 디스크 및 파티션 설정 : 그냥 다음을 눌러도 될 것 같았지만 전 직접 만들어줬습니다<br>\n<div class=\"imageblock center\" style=\"text-align: center; clear: both;\"><span data-url=\"https://t1.daumcdn.net/tistoryfile/fs13/16_tistory_2009_01_14_14_29_496d78200c7f7?x-content-disposition=inline\" data-lightbox=\"lightbox\"><img srcset=\"https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?scode=mtistory2&fname=https%3A%2F%2Ft1.daumcdn.net%2Ftistoryfile%2Ffs13%2F16_tistory_2009_01_14_14_29_496d78200c7f7%3Fx-content-disposition%3Dinline\" src=\"https://t1.daumcdn.net/tistoryfile/fs13/16_tistory_2009_01_14_14_29_496d78200c7f7?x-content-disposition=inline\" style=\"cursor: pointer;max-width:100%;height:auto\" width=\"510\" height=\"381\" alt=\"\" filename=\"screenshot15.png\" filemime=\"\" ></span></div><br>\n7. 설치가 진행됩니다.<br>\n<div class=\"imageblock center\" style=\"text-align: center; clear: both;\"><span data-url=\"https://t1.daumcdn.net/tistoryfile/fs13/12_tistory_2009_01_14_14_29_496d782042613?x-content-disposition=inline\" data-lightbox=\"lightbox\"><img srcset=\"https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?scode=mtistory2&fname=https%3A%2F%2Ft1.daumcdn.net%2Ftistoryfile%2Ffs13%2F12_tistory_2009_01_14_14_29_496d782042613%3Fx-content-disposition%3Dinline\" src=\"https://t1.daumcdn.net/tistoryfile/fs13/12_tistory_2009_01_14_14_29_496d782042613?x-content-disposition=inline\" style=\"cursor: pointer;max-width:100%;height:auto\" width=\"510\" height=\"380\" alt=\"\" filename=\"screenshot16.png\" filemime=\"\" ></span></div><br>\n8. 오~ 멋있어진 부팅화면... 이 때만 해도 설치가 다 된 줄 알았습니다.<br>\n<div class=\"imageblock center\" style=\"text-align: center; clear: both;\"><span data-url=\"https://t1.daumcdn.net/tistoryfile/fs13/15_tistory_2009_01_14_14_29_496d782076001?x-content-disposition=inline\" data-lightbox=\"lightbox\"><img srcset=\"https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?scode=mtistory2&fname=https%3A%2F%2Ft1.daumcdn.net%2Ftistoryfile%2Ffs13%2F15_tistory_2009_01_14_14_29_496d782076001%3Fx-content-disposition%3Dinline\" src=\"https://t1.daumcdn.net/tistoryfile/fs13/15_tistory_2009_01_14_14_29_496d782076001?x-content-disposition=inline\" style=\"cursor: pointer;max-width:100%;height:auto\" width=\"510\" height=\"380\" alt=\"\" filename=\"screenshot18.png\" filemime=\"\" ></span></div><br>\n9. 이제 Windows7을 만져보나 하는 순간!!!<br>\n<div class=\"imageblock center\" style=\"text-align: center; clear: both;\"><span data-url=\"https://t1.daumcdn.net/tistoryfile/fs13/6_tistory_2009_01_14_14_29_496d78209e79a?x-content-disposition=inline\" data-lightbox=\"lightbox\"><img srcset=\"https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?scode=mtistory2&fname=https%3A%2F%2Ft1.daumcdn.net%2Ftistoryfile%2Ffs13%2F6_tistory_2009_01_14_14_29_496d78209e79a%3Fx-content-disposition%3Dinline\" src=\"https://t1.daumcdn.net/tistoryfile/fs13/6_tistory_2009_01_14_14_29_496d78209e79a?x-content-disposition=inline\" style=\"cursor: pointer;max-width:100%;height:auto\" width=\"510\" height=\"381\" alt=\"\" filename=\"screenshot20.png\" filemime=\"\" ></span></div><br>\n10. 설치가 계속됩니다. Windows의 설치는 예나 지금이나 비슷하네요. :)<br>\n<div class=\"imageblock center\" style=\"text-align: center; clear: both;\"><span data-url=\"https://t1.daumcdn.net/tistoryfile/fs13/6_tistory_2009_01_14_14_29_496d7820c7bbf?x-content-disposition=inline\" data-lightbox=\"lightbox\"><img srcset=\"https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?scode=mtistory2&fname=https%3A%2F%2Ft1.daumcdn.net%2Ftistoryfile%2Ffs13%2F6_tistory_2009_01_14_14_29_496d7820c7bbf%3Fx-content-disposition%3Dinline\" src=\"https://t1.daumcdn.net/tistoryfile/fs13/6_tistory_2009_01_14_14_29_496d7820c7bbf?x-content-disposition=inline\" style=\"cursor: pointer;max-width:100%;height:auto\" width=\"510\" height=\"382\" alt=\"\" filename=\"screenshot21.png\" filemime=\"\" ></span></div><br>\n11. 드디어 사용자 ID 입력하고 비밀번호 입력하는 곳이 나왔습니다.<br>\n<div class=\"imageblock center\" style=\"text-align: center; clear: both;\"><span data-url=\"https://t1.daumcdn.net/tistoryfile/fs13/17_tistory_2009_01_14_14_29_496d7820d9ccd?x-content-disposition=inline\" data-lightbox=\"lightbox\"><img srcset=\"https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?scode=mtistory2&fname=https%3A%2F%2Ft1.daumcdn.net%2Ftistoryfile%2Ffs13%2F17_tistory_2009_01_14_14_29_496d7820d9ccd%3Fx-content-disposition%3Dinline\" src=\"https://t1.daumcdn.net/tistoryfile/fs13/17_tistory_2009_01_14_14_29_496d7820d9ccd?x-content-disposition=inline\" style=\"cursor: pointer;max-width:100%;height:auto\" width=\"510\" height=\"380\" alt=\"\" filename=\"screenshot22.png\" filemime=\"\" ></span></div><div class=\"imageblock center\" style=\"text-align: center; clear: both;\"><span data-url=\"https://t1.daumcdn.net/tistoryfile/fs13/22_tistory_2009_01_14_14_29_496d78211c970?x-content-disposition=inline\" data-lightbox=\"lightbox\"><img srcset=\"https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?scode=mtistory2&fname=https%3A%2F%2Ft1.daumcdn.net%2Ftistoryfile%2Ffs13%2F22_tistory_2009_01_14_14_29_496d78211c970%3Fx-content-disposition%3Dinline\" src=\"https://t1.daumcdn.net/tistoryfile/fs13/22_tistory_2009_01_14_14_29_496d78211c970?x-content-disposition=inline\" style=\"cursor: pointer;max-width:100%;height:auto\" width=\"510\" height=\"380\" alt=\"\" filename=\"screenshot23.png\" filemime=\"\" ></span></div><br>\n12. 엇! 정상적인 경로로 얻은 이미지가 아니라 cd-key 같은건 모르는데...<br>\n그냥 다음을 눌렀더니....<br>\n<div class=\"imageblock center\" style=\"text-align: center; clear: both;\"><span data-url=\"https://t1.daumcdn.net/tistoryfile/fs13/26_tistory_2009_01_14_14_29_496d782157ea0?x-content-disposition=inline\" data-lightbox=\"lightbox\"><img srcset=\"https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?scode=mtistory2&fname=https%3A%2F%2Ft1.daumcdn.net%2Ftistoryfile%2Ffs13%2F26_tistory_2009_01_14_14_29_496d782157ea0%3Fx-content-disposition%3Dinline\" src=\"https://t1.daumcdn.net/tistoryfile/fs13/26_tistory_2009_01_14_14_29_496d782157ea0?x-content-disposition=inline\" style=\"cursor: pointer;max-width:100%;height:auto\" width=\"510\" height=\"381\" alt=\"\" filename=\"screenshot24.png\" filemime=\"\" ></span></div><br>\n13. 잘 되네요. :) 아무래도 인터넷 Activation 인가 뭔가로 진행될 듯합니다.<br>\n<div class=\"imageblock center\" style=\"text-align: center; clear: both;\"><span data-url=\"https://t1.daumcdn.net/tistoryfile/fs13/29_tistory_2009_01_14_14_29_496d7821a94a3?x-content-disposition=inline\" data-lightbox=\"lightbox\"><img srcset=\"https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?scode=mtistory2&fname=https%3A%2F%2Ft1.daumcdn.net%2Ftistoryfile%2Ffs13%2F29_tistory_2009_01_14_14_29_496d7821a94a3%3Fx-content-disposition%3Dinline\" src=\"https://t1.daumcdn.net/tistoryfile/fs13/29_tistory_2009_01_14_14_29_496d7821a94a3?x-content-disposition=inline\" style=\"cursor: pointer;max-width:100%;height:auto\" width=\"510\" height=\"382\" alt=\"\" filename=\"screenshot25.png\" filemime=\"\" ></span></div><br>\n14. 시간을 설정하는 부분입니다.<br>\n<div class=\"imageblock center\" style=\"text-align: center; clear: both;\"><span data-url=\"https://t1.daumcdn.net/tistoryfile/fs13/16_tistory_2009_01_14_14_29_496d782256941?x-content-disposition=inline\" data-lightbox=\"lightbox\"><img srcset=\"https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?scode=mtistory2&fname=https%3A%2F%2Ft1.daumcdn.net%2Ftistoryfile%2Ffs13%2F16_tistory_2009_01_14_14_29_496d782256941%3Fx-content-disposition%3Dinline\" src=\"https://t1.daumcdn.net/tistoryfile/fs13/16_tistory_2009_01_14_14_29_496d782256941?x-content-disposition=inline\" style=\"cursor: pointer;max-width:100%;height:auto\" width=\"510\" height=\"381\" alt=\"\" filename=\"screenshot26.png\" filemime=\"\" ></span></div><br>\n15. 이제 정말 시작되려나 봅니다.<br>\n<div class=\"imageblock center\" style=\"text-align: center; clear: both;\"><span data-url=\"https://t1.daumcdn.net/tistoryfile/fs13/16_tistory_2009_01_14_14_29_496d782269e6c?x-content-disposition=inline\" data-lightbox=\"lightbox\"><img srcset=\"https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?scode=mtistory2&fname=https%3A%2F%2Ft1.daumcdn.net%2Ftistoryfile%2Ffs13%2F16_tistory_2009_01_14_14_29_496d782269e6c%3Fx-content-disposition%3Dinline\" src=\"https://t1.daumcdn.net/tistoryfile/fs13/16_tistory_2009_01_14_14_29_496d782269e6c?x-content-disposition=inline\" style=\"cursor: pointer;max-width:100%;height:auto\" width=\"510\" height=\"381\" alt=\"\" filename=\"screenshot27.png\" filemime=\"\" ></span></div><br>\n16. 진짜 모습을 드러냈습니다. Windows7<br>\n<div class=\"imageblock center\" style=\"text-align: center; clear: both;\"><span data-url=\"https://t1.daumcdn.net/tistoryfile/fs13/8_tistory_2009_01_14_14_29_496d782288013?x-content-disposition=inline\" data-lightbox=\"lightbox\"><img srcset=\"https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?scode=mtistory2&fname=https%3A%2F%2Ft1.daumcdn.net%2Ftistoryfile%2Ffs13%2F8_tistory_2009_01_14_14_29_496d782288013%3Fx-content-disposition%3Dinline\" src=\"https://t1.daumcdn.net/tistoryfile/fs13/8_tistory_2009_01_14_14_29_496d782288013?x-content-disposition=inline\" style=\"cursor: pointer;max-width:100%;height:auto\" width=\"510\" height=\"383\" alt=\"\" filename=\"screenshot28.png\" filemime=\"\" ></span></div><br>\nUbuntu에 설치한 VirtualBox에 설치했는데 OS는 Windows Vista로 선택했습니다. 그랬더니 잘 되네요. :)<br>\n그나저나 게스트 OS 설치같은 것이 안되고, 인터넷도 안되는 관계로..<br>\n더이상의 테스트는... 불가... 이제 천천히 알아가 보죠. 뭐... Vista도 잘 모르긴 하지만.. :)<br>\n<br>            ","summary":"Windows의 새버전을 체험할 수 있도록 MS에서 다운로드를 할 수 있다기에 한번 다운로드 받아서 설치해보았습니다. 물론 남아도는 (좋은 사양의) 컴퓨터가 없기때문에 가장 성능좋은 컴퓨터에 VirtualBox로 설치했습니다.\n1. 부팅\n\n2. 언어 및 입력기 설정 (언어는 영어뿐이지만 입력기는 한글이 가능하네요)\n\n3. 설치 시작\n\n4. 라이센스에 동의하라! 는 말이..\n\n5. Upgrade할지 Custom 설치를 할지 물어보는데 Upgrade를 선택","image":"https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R800x0/?scode=mtistory2&fname=https%3A%2F%2Ft1.daumcdn.net%2Ftistoryfile%2Ffs13%2F24_tistory_2009_01_14_14_28_496d781a8a652%3Foriginal"}},"__N_SSG":true}